# Torque Curve Visualizer

This kivy app utilizes matplotlib to visualize torque, horsepower and wheel torque curves from data passed in through json files.
## Features

- Import data from json files
- Visualize Torque and Horsepower curves on a graph
- If neccessary data is provided, visualize per gear Wheel Torque on a graph
- Export these graphs as images
- Edit Gear Ratios and Differential/Final Drive Ratio and see changes in real time